<collectingRegion box="[360,514,686,709]" country="Thailand" name="Loei" pageId="3" pageNumber="210">Loei Province</collectingRegion>
) by 
<bibRefCitation author="BAEHR, M. &amp; BAEHR, B." box="[563,810,686,709]" pageId="3" pageNumber="210" pagination="1 - 95" refId="ref5604" refString="BAEHR, M. &amp; BAEHR, B. 1993. The Hersiliidae of the Oriental Region including New Guinea. Taxonomy, phylogeny, zoogeography (Arachnida, Araneae). Spixiana Supplement 19: 1 - 95." type="journal article" year="1993">Baehr &amp; Baehr (1993)</bibRefCitation>
